STATE EX REL. FREED
v.
DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL 2018-0609 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 24, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

In Mandamus. On relator's motion for articulation and motion for Ohio Constitution, Article IV, Section 2 (C) "reasons therefor." Motions denied. Respondent's motion to strike motion for articulation denied.
